attribute.description:
F0RC08: Input/Output Configuration Control Word; mss_eff_cnfg will set Default value - 0x03. Values Range from 00 to 08 decimal. Check the stack height and calculate dynamically; 00 = Stack height_8; 01 = Stack height_4;
        02 = Stack height_2;
creator: mss_eff_cnfg
consumer: mss_dram_init
firmware notes: none
